Emotion Detector project
========================

Files
-----
- `facial_expression_recognizer.py` -> Kivy app code for APK packaging
- `main.py` -> entry point used by Buildozer
- `buildozer.spec` -> Android APK build configuration

Build APK on Windows using WSL Ubuntu
-------------------------------------
1. Install WSL:
   `wsl --install -d Ubuntu`
2. In Ubuntu, open this folder and install tools:
   `sudo apt update`
   `sudo apt install -y python3-pip python3-venv git zip unzip openjdk-17-jdk`
   `pip install --upgrade pip`
   `pip install buildozer cython`
3. Build the APK:
   `buildozer android debug`
4. Find the generated file in the `bin/` folder.

Important
---------
This mobile version is an APK-ready starter with camera preview. For real emotion
recognition on Android, replace the placeholder with a TensorFlow Lite model.
